room_title: Escape room "Mission Impossible" by My Greatest Escape in Ventura
room_address: 15500 W Telegraph Rd #15 Santa Paula, CA 93060
room_description: You are a special agent assigned to a secret squad that uses time travel to solve old murders. A rogue agent’s wife and two kids were murdered as a result of a case he was working on. He blames the agency and the time machine and is now set for vengeance. He plans to destroy the Time Machine and everything it stands for. Your mission is to enter the forensic lab, find the device and defuse it, before it’s too late.
